headline: The Mosaic Company (MOS) Beat the Market in 2025 on Strong Phosphate and Potash Sales
summary: The Mosaic Company (NYSE:MOS) is one of the Best Dividend Stocks of 2025. The company raised its potash production plans for 2025 to meet rising international demand.
